M|Qual|it|Zero rt w/o Zod validation on all inputs
M|Qual|it|Zero rt that expose ap keys to the client
M|Qual|it|Zero sb queries w/o an explicit RLS consideration documented
M|Qual|it|Zero cron rt w/o CRON_SECRET validation before handler body
M|Qual|it|Zero unhandled Promise rejections in rt handlers
